    "Search based repair suffers from the more serious issue of test-data overfitting where the generated repair can pass the given tests, but not other tests.The issue of overfitting in program repair, and specifically search-based program repair has been mentioned in [120] Constraint-based program repair approaches mitigate these concerns, by constructing a generalization of given tests via symbolic analysis.Constraint-based Program Repair."
